{"tid":474622,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Bobby 搞 到 吳 業 坤「 戚 袋 袋 」","createTime":"2017-11-20T10:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T11:04:03.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6edfcbd929ef43180eba78460d59832429734fef","tid":474622,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T10:51:49.000Z","msg":"歐陽震華(Bobby)、張繼聰、吳業坤、陳豪及田蕊妮等，昨日為劇集《誇世代》宣傳，眾人大玩攀石及滑梯，一眾男藝人由於要戴上安全帶，下體即時玲瓏浮凸，Bobby即說：「今次真係現代嘞！」貪玩的他，更走到吳業坤身邊，大力拉緊他的安全帶，並笑說：「呢單Big Deal嚟！」令「戚袋袋」的吳業坤，面露痛苦神情後，即尷尬傻笑並以雙手遮掩下體。問Bobby為何戴上太陽眼鏡，他解釋：「好似想生眼瘡，唔夠瞓啩，可能呢排睇得靚嘢多。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2017/11/1510857869_Xt-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2017%2F11%2F1510857869_Xt-1280w.jpg&h=258ea1a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33d73853e7f73f58c8bf0885e8ea4898f9ee4533","tid":474622,"uid":86756,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T10:53:23.000Z","msg":"Eason 玩會唔會輕鬆d"},{"pid":"b3baefdb2d4123723fa4619350b78881122ffe2c","tid":474622,"uid":17606,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T10:57:59.000Z","msg":"男提老狗著黑絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a25fe0d7ba586f8edae89a755be0787eb38eebe","tid":474622,"uid":23445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T11:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Eason 玩會唔會輕鬆d</blockquote><br />\nEason 睬你都有味<br />\n玩呢d,陣間爆埋另外一粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}